The system uses a fork of IRRemote that adds ESP32 support (https://github.com/ExploreEmbedded/Arduino-IRremote).  In the file boarddefs.h, the
value of TIMER_PWM_PIN (line 565) was changed to 12.

The library csscolorparser included in the source directory isn't an Arduino library, so was included with the source.  It's GitHub repository can be found
at https://github.com/mapbox/css-color-parser-cpp.